cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses optimization algorithms in robotics, which falls under the category of robotics and automation (cs.RO). The use of regression algorithms to learn the transferability function suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of the reality gap and fitness landscapes also involves systems and control (cs.SY) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
